    "body" : "<p>If you are actually looking for Charting libraries and not for Node/Edge Graph libraries I would suggest splurging on Big Faceless Graph library (<a href=\"http://big.faceless.org/products/graph/\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">BFG</a>).  It's way easier to use than JFreeChart, looks nicer, runs faster, has more output options, really no comparison.</p>\n"
